      "message": "[🟡 Suggestion] Line 589: `setAccountsActive(false)` can explicitly deactivate non-proxy accounts, but it does not update `explicitlyDeactivatedAccounts`. If an account later has the proxy enabled while still inactive, the background optimization can record and restore it because the explicit marker is missing. Keep the explicit-deactivation tracking consistent for bulk activation changes.\n```suggestion\nif (active) {\n    explicitlyDeactivatedAccounts.clear()\n} else {\n    for (a in mAccountList) {\n        if (!a.isDhtProxyEnabled) explicitlyDeactivatedAccounts.add(a.accountId)\n    }\n}\n```",
